description: The Hyper Dimension Chain is rooted in the application field of the actual scene. Through the establishment of e-commerce platform and integration of e-commerce resources, various business developments are realized, including e-commerce APP development, logistics projects, media advertising, mediation, consumer goods traceability, various financial services, Other content such as supply chain management. As a token in the Hyper Dimension Chain ecosystem, HDCC will combine existing e-commerce and blockchain protocols to provide its customers with leading blockchain technology.
name: Hyper Dimension Chain
